data.description: Welcome home to Cutter Gap! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath mobile home sits on a permanent foundation in a non HOA community. Better than new with upgrades throughout. Enter into the living room and make your way to the open concept kitchen and dining area. The large laundry room off of the kitchen allows for extra storage space and dining area leads directly to the large deck overlooking the fenced in back yard. Storage shed shall convey with the property.
